###############################################################
# Bootstrap OAuth Mercado Livre (rodar 1x)
# OBS: o app sobe na porta 8081 (server.port no application.yml)
###############################################################

### 1a. Caminho rápido: injeta o refresh_token do .env direto no banco.
#       Se retornar erro (invalid_grant), use o Postman e o passo 1b.
POST http://localhost:8081/api/ml/auth/seed
Content-Type: application/json

{ "refreshToken": "TG-6a2d63ba7cb8d60001698890-1620572657" }

### 1b. Via Postman: cole aqui o refresh_token novo obtido no Postman.
POST http://localhost:8081/api/ml/auth/seed
Content-Type: application/json

{ "refreshToken": "COLE_O_REFRESH_TOKEN_DO_POSTMAN_AQUI" }

### 2. (opcional) Fluxo OAuth pelo próprio bot — só funciona com redirect_uri https.
#      Abra a urlAutorizacao retornada no navegador, logado como ADMIN.
GET http://localhost:8081/api/ml/auth/login

### 3. Validação: dispara o ciclo usando o token salvo no banco.
POST http://localhost:8081/api/mercadolivre/executar
